In 2015 he partnered up with Masoud Fuladi and started an Electronic dance music project called MaWayy and released his first single "Wrong" in August 2017 under Teletunez's division HitTunez and Blanco Y Negro record label includes remixes by Joe Maz and Ayin.
In May 2018 this song ranked No.42 on Billboard Dance Club Songs chart for three weeks.
